==Arabic alphabet==

===Letter===
{{ARchar|'''ح '''/''' ح‍ '''/''' ‍ح‍ '''/''' ‍ح'''}} (ħā’)

# The sixth letter of the [[Arabic]] alphabet. It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[ج]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[خ]]}}.
# The eighth letter in traditional [[abjad]] order, which is used in place of numerals for list numbering ([[abjad numerals]]). It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[ز]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[ط]]}}.

